data.description: This home is located walking distance to Cross Roads and very close to Valley View Mall, the airport and the interstate. It has a large updated kitchen with granite counter tops, hardwood floors and many upgrades. It has a side screened porch and the rear lawn is fenced. Room in lower level can be used as a 3rd bedroom/homeoffice.
